commit.message:
Plugins implementation has been refactored.

Previous implementation using pkg_resources has been replaced with a new
implementation using importlib.resources. Old plugins are now just
features that can be enabled/disabled by the user.

This move implies a number of changes:

- vitables/plugins folder renamed as vitables/extensions
- vitables/preferences/pluginsloader.py deleted
- modified in vitables/preferences: preferences.py, vtconfig.py and
  settings_dlg.ui
- modified vtapp.py
